      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried drinking some water but my tongue feels kinda heavy? and like i phrased things wrong when i tried to talk to the front desk. i'm kinda scared it's more than just being thirsty but i really dont want to go to a hospital in a foreign country if i don't have to. u sure it's just the heat?",
